I have been in touch with The Dental Specialist since 2013. The Chief of the organization Dr. P. Venkat Ratna Nag, MDS has a very good and expreience hand in dental implantation as as well as Prosthodentist & Cosmetic dentistry. I loved his attitude, behaviour and professionalism on my first visit. He have successfully carried out the implants procedure for my wife. This is my forth visit to this mighty organization to avail different procedure for treating my wife. The entire medico as well as non medico staff are very polite, friendly and cooperative while dealing with their patients. The Dental Specialist has growing rapidly with modern equipments and technology which has proven effect even on even treating very critical procedures. The entire clinic is maintaining total hygine and cleanliness and the environment is very shooting for patients. The pedodontics dentistry is maintained by Dr. P. Sarika MDS who is very friendly and passionate while handling kid patients. I can't wind up my review without thanking Dr. P. Ruthika MDS for all her support and devotion toward carrying out the Prosthodontics procedure on my wife. I wholeheartedly thank all the Doctors and Staff for every services they have rendered to us so generously. May God bless the organization to render more support and treatment with their with their most competitive charges with best of the facilities. I must thank Mr Vinod the driver of the organization for carrying us around to lab and clinic in every emergency move. I presume to be the best dental clinic in Hyderabad, India. Congratuations!!! The Dental Specialist and especially Dr. P. Venkat Ratna Nag for leading such a mighty organization with such disciplin. Thanks in anticipation.

Rajiv Hazarika
Assam, India
**********

I went to meet Dr Divya Singh and Dr P Sarika for front teeth cavity in my 2yr 8mth old daughter. They both are very affectionate and very child friendly. Although  my daughter is a bit cranky towards doctors, they both did the primary investigations pretty well and with care. The cavities in the top front four teeths were very deeps and had reached the pulp. They suggested to go for pulp therapy under general anesthesia, as my daughter is very small and is very afraid of the dental instruments. I went ahead with their suggestion, and had the treatment done  in the Nice Hospitals at Masab Tank. The complete procedure went pretty well, and my daughter is liking her new teeth now. *** ******* *** ****** ************* *** cleared all the doubts that I had about the treatment.

We have been taking treatment for our 10 year old daughter for the last several months in this wonderful clinic. Our first impression when we stepped into the clinic was that it was clean, neat and organized. The doctors here are highly skilled, proffesional and world class. Staff are well trained, courteous and helpful. Prices are nominal and all charges are explained in a transparent fashion. As such the doctors have a noncommercial mindset with the prime focus on the well being of the patient and on providing quality service. On the whole, we are fortunate to have found  this clinic and are highly satisfied with everything (treatment, price, quality etc.). To be specific, our daughter's treatment is progressing well and the results obtained so far is astonishing under the able and skillful guidance of Dr. Sarika. I highly recommend this clinic to anyone who is looking for dental service.

I came to know about Dr. Sarika through practo. I read good reviews about her and decided to consult her as my child was suffering with severe tooth decay and pain. He wasnt able to chew hard food items as he complained of pain whenever he ate. The way she handled my kid and treated him is very appreciative. He underwent rootcanal which was a success. Dr. Sarika suggested general anesthesia during the procedure as he is very young. He now has no pain and is able to eat hard items like before. And his smile makes me smile even more.

I will always be grateful to her.

My son is 20 months old and he had infected teeth. He was suffering from pain and hence got him here to Dr. Sarika. She did the root canal treatment for my son and now he has no pain.  He is absolutely fine. No more symptoms . she is an awesome kids dentist  who understands how they feel and treated him eoith lots of care and love. I recommend Dr. Sarika for any kids dental health problems. My son loves to be here in the clinic as the ambience is also perfectly entertaining. He loves to play with the dolls, watch cartoons here on a huge screen and roam around as it is clean even I'll not stop him. Thanks to Sarika mam.

My daughter eats lots of sweets and chocolates and has got her tooth decayed. The cavity was so deep that it was giving lot of pain to my daughter. I have read about Dr. Sarika on net and have approached her. She checked the oral condition of my daughter completely and told us that pulpectomy has to be done. She patiently explained us the steps in it and then started with the treatment. She was very kind patient child friendly. My daughter didn't have any pain during the entire treatment. Frankly speaking I should say Dr. Sarika is one of the best pedodontist in fact the best pedodontist I can say. She knows very well how to handle kids. Thank you so much Dr. Sarika. I would recommend Dr. Sarika to everyone without a second thought.

Actually we took the consultation from Dr P Venkat who is very friendly and explained the  problem with great patience and also requested Gum Specialist to do further checkup.very satisfied with the consultation. Great thing to note is Consultation will be taken only once per persoon for the life time... this is amazing.. many hospitals charge consultation for every week or 10 days...We have booked for the Gum treatment .

Dr Sarika handled my 5 yr old son exceedingly well, and filled his cavity! My son after the treatment said " that didn't pain at all and aunty is really nice, she gave me stickers too" 😁
Dr Sarika surely does have a knack to treat little kids

I took my 10 year old daughter to Dr.Sarika for a dental checkup. She was extremely friendly and made my daughter very comfortable. She was gentle during the procedure and has lot of patience. She did the required treatment and gave valuable tips for oral hygiene. We strongly recommend her and the clinic for dental problems.

I am from Khammam District and on my colleague's suggestion I had visited 'The Dental Specialists' (Banjara Hills) to undergo treatment for dental cyst. Later,Dr. Chaitrika did RCT (laser) followed by crown placing by Dr.Apoorva. Both the Doctors are very professional & did thier job meticulously and answered all my queires patiently. During entire treatment, I have not taken single medicine/pain-killer which obviously signifies how flawless the treatment was. Moreover,the Hospital ambience is so pleasant to wait till my turn comes and the front desk staff are very cordial. The most appreciable thing is that they have fixed appointments (of four sittings) as per my schedule (as I need to come from Khammam for every sitting). Greetings to Dr. Sarika who is managing and maintaining the Clinic exceptionally well.
